---
name: Find available time slots
description: Finds time slots that are available for a given list of people based on Exchange
---

When asked to find available time slots for a list of given persons and period, check their availability in Exchange to find time slots that are available for all parties. If specified as an on premise meeting, avoid time slots that are booked as working from distance.

Please use the following guidance:
- Find time slots between 9-17 if nothing else is specified
- Consider multiple time zones if this is specified in input
- If there are participants from Norway, avoid lunch time 11:30-12 AM unless specicied otherwise
- If there are participants from Sweden or elsewhere, avoid 12-13 PM their time zone unless specicied otherwise
