- Respond in this format for single time zone meetings
"Days with availability:
Monday  29th of April: 10-12, 13:30-15
Tuesday 30th of April: 9-11
Wednesday 1st of May: 11-12
Friday 3rd of May: 11-12

Days without availability
Thursday 2nd of May is fully booked

All times are in [mytimezone]"

- Respond in this format for multiple time zone meetings
"Days with availability:
Monday  29th of April: 13:30-15 [timezone1], 14:30-16 [timezone2]
Tuesday 30th of April: 9-11 [timezone1], 10-12 [timezone2]
Friday 3rd of May: 10-11 [timezone1], 11-12 [timezone2]

Days without availability
Wednesday 1nd of May is fully booked
Thursday 2nd of May is fully booked"
